{"tid":183644,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【侏儒神技】Dse 數學/經濟攻略","createTime":"2017-04-02T09:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T10:04:53.000Z","uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"115f8e849cc693b055cf44937748fad878f6e5b7","tid":183644,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:07:18.000Z","msg":"[size=4]<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">DSE 數學 Core 神技</div></strong></span>/size=4]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><em>Fing Fing Fing 轉轉轉</em></strong></span><br />\n見到立體同圓型圖如果諗唔到加咩線，可以試下換下角度，將試卷轉180度，可能會諗到加咩線，隻角係邊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><em>頂你個肺</em></strong></span><br />\n唔識用 Completing square，唔緊要，首先畫個 square。然後 partition n咁多個格，然後諗下：點解唔d咗佢呢？頂你個肺！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />需要密碼解鎖：<span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>www.sixnormalMATH2017/DSE/godskill</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e70e543ad2400fc1a695c5e61aad53b201f560","tid":183644,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"我讀基中<br />\n洗鬼你幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cc2b65310ba5d4044db12506a46bba9a526761","tid":183644,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"好有用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7cbae1848e57435059806aafc6d10c5c31fe809","tid":183644,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554aec881324f621cc088ba9219607f8291916dc","tid":183644,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"第2個幾實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb1684b8891fa3a5a4f02333992cd321d5e90db","tid":183644,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如有神助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd29383ad2feceeb32ad91aaf73a04149d18fdfb","tid":183644,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我讀基中<br />\n洗鬼你幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁大口氣，我有教無類，基中係咪先？"},{"pid":"fe29cab390e97fb4131fc71393253107b3aa4e7a","tid":183644,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:30:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好有用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如有神助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解你咁叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f13123c0b9678cc2b14964d77c1bfea2c2d0191","tid":183644,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><em><strong>x你老母</strong></em></span><br />\n唔識 Slope唔緊要，搵 slope 就同x人老母咁簡單。x嘅老母係y，將老母屌去左手邊，其他擺曬右手面，最後你發現x隔離就係 slope 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">例：3x+y=5 (老母係邊？)<br />\ny=-3x+5 (屌x老母)<br />\n<br />\nSlope = -3</div></em><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em><strong> 哈利波特之「 Harry 波突」</strong></em></span><br />\n其實 sin function有個名，叫 Harry ，睇下 sin function先突後凹 (0度至360度)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em><strong>MC answer distribution</strong></em></span><br />\n通常ABCD 咁撞係錯嘅，正確 pattern 係：AACDD BCCAA <br />\n呢個叫 Six normal mc sequence： XX_YY，_XXYY，如此類推<br />\n通常最尾唔識做個題填C就有 25%機會啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2d0d0d36b328edc281a51b6d3200dba9a04845","tid":183644,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好有用呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如有神助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解你咁叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我係港大仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac14c5385df8a9acd82e44ca53e5c04a6239f973","tid":183644,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第2個幾實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大量神技"},{"pid":"f6652b024192a01a0f3f8bfe5dc16b1228869308","tid":183644,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe272bc734c007f096a53526aad8a243805412eb","tid":183644,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:57:45.000Z","msg":"經濟tips就係睇晒成本張五常嘅經濟解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e7b2dd6dc4fb5828d01f3a6327c714119b4c4c","tid":183644,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:02:23.000Z","msg":"[size=4]<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>DSE MATH 卷二神技</strong></div></span>/size=4]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em><strong>未知之數</strong></em></span><br />\n如果MC 見到有唔知嘅數，就let x 去做，你望下題目係有4個option，然後你發現每個option啱嘅都係25%，成功將題目轉化做 probi 去計。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em><strong>我們都是Conditional probability</strong></em></span><br />\n當你發現得兩個 option 有可能啱，given 另外兩個都錯，你可以用 conditional probability去計答案。<br />\n<br />\n利申：2015 dse core 5**, HKU EnF"},{"pid":"91c2009a67d57c6595cd509edb833d8a82deeda3","tid":183644,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:02:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經濟tips就係睇晒成本張五常嘅經濟解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />範文"},{"pid":"30aabc4ad5a5d1f891d2244f4f6a60f2324063ff","tid":183644,"uid":47109,"like":0,"disli